title: IWBAN
name: Inside Wire Billing Account Number
definition: Identifies the previously assigned Billing Account Number for charges associated with inside wire.
usageNotes:
Required  w hen the GETO field on the service specific form is "A", "E", "S", "T", "U", "V", "W", "Y", or "Z". 
Prohibited when the ACT field is "D". 
Otherwise optional.
